title: Tornado Meme contest, choose your winner
body:
It is now time to vote for the 3 best memes !

As a reminder, there will be 3 winners in this competition, and here is the prize list:

#1: `15 TORN`

#2: `8 TORN`

#3: `4 TORN`

After thinking with the multisig team regarding how we could manage this amount of participations, we agreed on the fact that it was necessary to make a short list before creating a snapshot, because it was impossible to set up a healthy vote with more than 100 participations.
Therefore, the snapshot is based on this short list, which the multisig team estimated as the 9 best contributions (arranged in ascending order of participation time).
